WebService::Thumbalizr
======================

Perl extension for Thumbalizr http://www.thumbalizr.com/, a web service to create website screenshots in real-time.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  URI::Escape
  Digest::MD5
  LWP::UserAgent

SOURCE

The source code is available on github at https://github.com/juliensobrier/WebService-Thumbalizr

CPAN

The library is available on CPAN at https://metacpan.org/pod/WebService::Thumbalizr

